| **Sample** | 516 women from 525 beneficiary households |
| **Collection method** | Cross-sectional household survey |
| **Study population** | Women of reproductive age in FNGAP beneficiary households |
| **Location & period** | Siraha, Saptari, and Udaypur districts, Madhesh Province, Nepal |

